                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Peace Treaty With Italy</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council continued the discussion in second reading of the un-agreed Articles
                    of the Italian Treaty.</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="italic">Article 16, Free Territory of Trieste</hi>.</p>
                <p>The discussion of the amendments to this Article proposed by the U.S.S.R,
                    Delegation, set out in Document <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46)
                        (NY)</gloss>13,<note n="19" xml:id="d328fn19">
                        <hi rend="italic">Infra</hi>.</note> was resumed.</p>
                <p>After a further exchange of views on the respective powers of the Governor and
                    the Council of Government in the Free Territory, the discussion was <hi
                        rend="italic">adjourned</hi>.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Newt Meeting of the Council</hi>.</p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">agreed</hi> to hold a private meeting of the Council on
                    Friday, November 15, at 4 p.m.</p>
